sky.engine.graphics.bounds
Class BoundingPoly

java.lang.Object
  sky.engine.graphics.bounds.Bounding
      sky.engine.graphics.bounds.BoundingPoly
Direct Known Subclasses:
BoundingBox, BoundingTri
public class BoundingPoly
extends Bounding

Bounding Polygons are to be created to bound more complicated objects. In general, Bounding Polygons should be convex. If a concave one is to be constructed, you should be wise to triangulate it.

Author:
Matthew Kelly (Badgerati).
